Note on OpenFront.io

This project is an independent, clean-room reimplementation of certain
publicly observable gameplay mechanics and numeric balancing found in
openfront.io, which is itself licensed under the GNU Affero General Public
License v3.0 (AGPL-3.0).

No source code or art assets from openfront.io are included in, or were used
to produce, this project. Game rules, mechanics, and numeric formulas are
facts and are not subject to copyright protection; only a work's specific
creative expression (source code, art, text) is protected. AGPL-3.0 governs
OpenFront's own expression — none of which appears in this repository.

See docs/openfront-balance-replication-plan.md for this project's clean-room
methodology and sourcing notes.
